Everything is ok in ipython, python and pdb.set_trace command lines.

Tested in terminal, terminator and text terminal (ctrl-alt-f1), using bash and zsh.

Reproduced by another user:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/35671018/home-button-bug-in-ipdb-on-ubuntu",{},{}
