413,IssuesEvent,2018-01-21 19:53:06+00:00,44054354,dabeaz/curio,350836,dabeaz,,,closed,Document exceptions raised by Kernel.run,[],[],11,"It seems that curio.run() may raise a TaskError. This is currently not documented, the documentation for Kernel.run does not mention any exceptions, and the documentation for TaskError states that this is only raised by a taks's join() method.

