1224,IssuesEvent,2017-12-17 10:15:40+00:00,73685532,lawsie/guizero,2329501,martinohanlon,,,closed,"App enable, disable, hide, show",[],[],7,"The functions enable, disable, hide, show within _Widget dont work with App.

I would suggest we refactor _Widget to group the functions into a number of Mixins e.g. 
- after, repeat, cancel
- enable, disable
- show, hide
- destroy
- focus

these can be inherited into the guizero components as appropriate e.g.
- PushButton(AfterRepeatCancel, EnableDisable, ShowHide, Destroy, Focus)
- App(AfterRepeatCancel, Destroy)

Happy to pick this up.
",{},{}
