2581,IssuesEvent,2017-10-23 15:49:38+00:00,2909429,nicolargo/glances,776747,nicolargo,,,opened,"Make enable, disable and export CLI option dynamical ",[],[],0,"#### Description

In Glances < 3.0, if you want to disable one or more plugin you should enter the following command line:

     glances --disable-network --disable-load

The current enhancement request proposes replace it by:

    glances --disable network,load

The new syntax will bring some dynamic function for the developper. When a new plugin is added, no more need to declare it in the main.py script.

#### Versions

* Glances (glances -V): Target release 3.0

#### Notes

Break the command line compatibility.",{},{}
