2616,IssuesEvent,2018-08-05 08:30:31+00:00,2909429,nicolargo/glances,776747,nicolargo,,,closed,Add disk I/O throughput requests per second,"[{'id': 204819, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWwyMDQ4MTk=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/nicolargo/glances/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '207de5', 'default': True}]",[],1,"#### Description

