2958,IssuesEvent,2018-03-30 15:47:26+00:00,59235,mkleehammer/pyodbc,27421,mkleehammer,,,closed,pyodbc insert/update failure with freetds on SQL Server 2014,[],[],1,"- Python: 3.4.2
