4657,IssuesEvent,2016-12-07 09:52:46+00:00,24529855,goldmann/docker-squash,43489,goldmann,,,closed,Add option for squashing all layers starting from the base image,[],[],2,"Currently there is an option to specify the hash of a specific layer from which you want to begin squashing, but it would be convenient if there was some short-hand way to detect which hash represents the base image and use that value automatically.

