Compared to other networks with subclass of **CustomOp** that **backward** function works well, I used symbols **slice_axis** and **concat** in this network, dose it matter?

I worked on windows 7,  the mxnet 0.9.5 is compiled with vs2013 and installed in python 2.7.
",{},{}
