7526,IssuesEvent,2017-12-11 23:16:02+00:00,52136436,sendgrid/python-http-client,169448,mbernier,181234,sendgrid,closed,Add a PEP8 check to travis.yml,"[{'id': 674389884, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/sendgrid/python-http-client/labels/difficulty:%20easy', 'name': 'difficulty: easy', 'color': 'f9d0c4', 'default': False}, {'id': 707352402, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/sendgrid/python-http-client/labels/hacktoberfest', 'name': 'hacktoberfest', 'color': 'fbca04', 'default': False}, {'id': 726230916, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/sendgrid/python-http-client/labels/help%20wanted', 'name': 'help wanted', 'color': 'ededed', 'default': True}, {'id': 726230915, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/sendgrid/python-http-client/labels/up-for-grabs', 'name': 'up-for-grabs', 'color': 'ededed', 'default': False}]",[],2,"#### Issue Summary

