8327,IssuesEvent,2017-04-19 09:40:21+00:00,2625205,robotframework/Selenium2Library,13982587,x64joxer,574284,robotframework,opened,Mouse right click,[],[],0,"It looks like Selenium supports right click mouse on element.
Selenium library in Robot Framework supports only left mouse click or context menu.
