8557,IssuesEvent,2017-07-14 03:02:59+00:00,54980593,pypa/setuptools,308610,jaraco,647025,pypa,closed,Deploys failing due to bootstrapping issues,[],[],2,"Since the acceptance of #1053, the tagged commits are now [failing to deploy thus](https://travis-ci.org/pypa/setuptools/jobs/253451649).

