8579,IssuesEvent,2018-02-15 01:47:05+00:00,1446474,pypa/virtualenv,5559355,Vandivier,647025,pypa,opened,git bash and documentation problems,[],[],0,"issue 1:  the ""edit on GitHub"" link is broken on [User Guide > Usage
