Hi,

I was using skimage to perform watershed segmentation, but the results were strange. I compared skimage implementation with my own  watershed implementation, and they don't agree. I looked at skimage code at https://github.com/scikit-image/scikit-image/blob/master/skimage/morphology/watershed.py#L35. 

I saw there is a pedagogical purely python implementation, and I analyzed the algorithm, and it seemed correct, so I compared the pedagogical implementation against mine. This time the results were the same. 

I believe there is a bug in the current Cython implementation. Attached are the results I got using the skimage code and my own.

