9119,IssuesEvent,2015-02-04 23:49:04+00:00,16366081,numenta/nupic.core,15566,rhyolight,1039191,numenta,opened,"Before building, run a check for requirement components and environments","[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/numenta/nupic.core/labels/build', 'name': 'build', 'color': '006b75'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/numenta/nupic.core/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/numenta/nupic.core/labels/P3', 'name': 'P3', 'color': '009800'}]",[],0,"Like many C projects have a `configure` step that informs the installer if there are any missing or misconfigured components of the user's environment before running the installation, I think we should put something similar in place for NuPIC.

