9415,IssuesEvent,2018-02-21 16:11:54+00:00,62325478,Linaro/squad,646015,situmam,1180626,Linaro,opened,List the groups first on the home page,[],[],0,"Right now, the group name is repeated with every job listed on the home page. In the case of qa-reports.linaro.org, the home page is quite cluttered. It would be much cleaner to have the home page default to the list of groups and have their projects listed as bullets. Adding expand/collapse visual UI would be ideal as well and making that persistent across sessions is ideal.",{},{}
