10191,IssuesEvent,2018-04-20 11:55:30+00:00,3470471,FortAwesome/Font-Awesome,38559736,DaniyyelMattay,1505683,FortAwesome,opened,Icon request: rfid,[],[],0,"### What can it be used for?

