11633,IssuesEvent,2017-01-13 10:20:05+00:00,70530854,awslabs/serverless-application-model,756733,Pelto,3299148,awslabs,opened,Not possible to have CodeUri as a parameter,[],[],0,"I have an issue in a sam template. 

