11636,IssuesEvent,2017-05-25 19:03:37+00:00,70530854,awslabs/serverless-application-model,188004,syang,3299148,awslabs,opened,Can implicit API-Gateway definition from Lambda function definition have custom authorizer?,[],[],0,"If I'd like to define my API-Gateway through an 'implicit way', i.e., by defining the Lambda function and its associated Events-->ApiEventSource. See an example below.

