13196,IssuesEvent,2016-11-18 19:17:12+00:00,51040886,Azure/azure-cli,124302,jmspring,6844498,Azure,opened,"CLI inconsistency -- to specify a parameters file, one must not use equal sign",[],[],0,"If you use an equal sign between --parameters and the actual file path, you end up with the following:

```
az resource group deployment create --resource-group=jmsdcosrg --template-file=./output/azuredeploy.json --parameters=""@./output/azuredeploy.parameters.json""
No JSON object could be decoded
```

Removing the equal sign works:

