15028,IssuesEvent,2018-07-12 01:35:15+00:00,112676803,apple/turicreate,5420744,TobyRoseman,10639145,apple,opened,libTuriCreate.dylib does not contain the right symbols.,"[{'id': 766077328, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw3NjYwNzczMjg=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/apple/turicreate/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'ee0701', 'default': True}]",[],0,"After running `build_capi.sh`, it does not look like the right symbols are being exported in libTuriCreate.dylib or in the framework. For example, the following command finds nothing:  `nm target/capi/libTuriCreate.dylib | grep -I sarray`. Looking at `nm target/capi/libTuriCreate.dylib` seems it's missing pretty much all of the symbols.",{},{}
