18365,IssuesEvent,2018-04-10 01:51:06+00:00,102692863,onnx/onnx,9300575,bddppq,31675368,onnx,closed,Gemm inputs of Inception v1/v2 inconsistent with ONNX spec,[],"[{'login': 'houseroad', 'id': 30275821, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/30275821?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/houseroad', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/houseroad/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",5,"In ONNX tests [Inception v1](https://github.com/onnx/onnx/blob/5716e2076b445b6c5bd017aaadc05d59ac43bdc3/onnx/backend/test/data/real/test_inception_v1) and [Inception v2](https://github.com/onnx/onnx/blob/5716e2076b445b6c5bd017aaadc05d59ac43bdc3/onnx/backend/test/data/real/test_inception_v2), the first input to GEMM op has 4 dimensions while the [ONNX spec](https://github.com/onnx/onnx/blob/master/docs/Operators.md#Gemm) states it should have only 2 dimensions. A possible quick fix would be inserting a reshape node before Gemm node. More fundamental changes might be needed in the model converter that produces this model.

Could someone take a look at it?

Thanks.
",{},{}
